</li>
<li class="rss-item"><a class="rss-item" href="http://feeds.nbcnews.com/c/35002/f/663301/s/3048b4dd/sc/30/l/0L0Snbcnews0N0Cbusiness0Cfederal0Ecourt0Econsumers0Ecan0Eprevent0Erobocalls0E6C10A9810A35/story01.htm"  title="Consumers have a right under a federal law to revoke their c..." target="_blank">Federal court: Consumers can prevent robocalls</a> <br />
Consumers have a right under a federal law to revoke their consent to being contacted on their cell phones by automated dialing systems, a U.S. appeals court decided on Thursday in a defeat for computer maker Dell Inc. Reversing a lower court ruling, the 3rd U.S.<img width='1' height='1' src='http://feeds.nbcnews.com/c/35002/f/663301/s/3048b4dd/sc/30/mf.gif' border='0'/><br clear='all'/><br/><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608229396/u/53/f/663301/c/35002/s/3048b4dd/sc/30/rc/1/rc.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608229396/u/53/f/663301/c/35002/s/3048b4dd/sc/30/rc/1/rc.img" border="0"/></a><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608229396/u/53/f/663301/c/35002/s/3048b4dd/sc/30/rc/2/rc.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608229396/u/53/f/663301/c/35002/s/3048b4dd/sc/30/rc/2/rc.img" border="0"/></a><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608229396/u/53/f/663301/c/35002/s/3048b4dd/sc/30/rc/3/rc.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608229396/u/53/f/663301/c/35002/s/3048b4dd/sc/30/rc/3/rc.img" border="0"/></a><br/><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608229396/u/53/f/663301/c/35002/s/3048b4dd/a2.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/173608229396/u/53/f/663301/c/35002/s/3048b4dd/a2.img" border="0"/></a><img width="1" height="1" src="http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/173608229396/u/53/f/663301/c/35002/s/3048b4dd/a2t.img" border="0"/>
</li>
